
# Swiss Unihockey API v2 — confirmed working endpoints
# KD Jets club_id: 463785
# Damen L-UPL:  league=24, game_class=21
# Herren L-UPL: league=24, game_class=11

### All seasons (dropdown; highlighted = upcoming registration season)
GET https://api-v2.swissunihockey.ch/api/seasons
Accept: application/json

### All leagues for a season (returns league + game_class IDs)
GET https://api-v2.swissunihockey.ch/api/leagues?season=2025&format=dropdown
Accept: application/json

### All clubs (Jets = 463785)
GET https://api-v2.swissunihockey.ch/api/clubs
Accept: application/json

### All Jets games for a season (scores, venues, league names)
GET https://api-v2.swissunihockey.ch/api/games?mode=club&club_id=463785&season=2025
Accept: application/json

### Full Damen L-UPL schedule for a season
GET https://api-v2.swissunihockey.ch/api/games?mode=list&season=2025&league=24&game_class=21
Accept: application/json

### Damen L-UPL standings
GET https://api-v2.swissunihockey.ch/api/rankings?season=2025&league=24&game_class=21
Accept: application/json

### Herren L-UPL standings
GET https://api-v2.swissunihockey.ch/api/rankings?season=2025&league=24&game_class=11
Accept: application/json

### Men's L-UPL top scorers (includes player IDs; women's equivalent unknown)
GET https://api-v2.swissunihockey.ch/api/topscorers/su?season=2025&amount=50
Accept: application/json

### Player profile by ID (position, birth year, height, club)
GET https://api-v2.swissunihockey.ch/api/players/521510
Accept: application/json

### Player game-by-game stats (goals, assists, points, PIM per game)
GET https://api-v2.swissunihockey.ch/api/players/521510/overview
Accept: application/json

### Game events — returns 404 for most games (requires partner access)
GET https://api-v2.swissunihockey.ch/api/game_events?game_id=1096886
Accept: application/json

### Teams in same league as Jets for a season (returns league peers, not just Jets roster)
GET https://api-v2.swissunihockey.ch/api/teams?club_id=463785&season=2025
Accept: application/json


