GET https://api-v2.swissunihockey.ch/api/game_events/1093736

### GET game summary  by game_id
GET https://api-v2.swissunihockey.ch/api/games/1096880/summary

### GET game_events by game_id 
GET https://api-v2.swissunihockey.ch/api/game_events/1096880


