Accept: application/json

### U14B Gruppe 9 standings via LeagueID 8568
GET https://api-v2.swissunihockey.ch/api/rankings?season=2025&league=8568
Accept: application/json

### GameID cross-check — 6-digit private API GameID against public API (expect 404 if different namespace)
GET https://api-v2.swissunihockey.ch/api/games/105916
Accept: application/json

